---
title: Creamy Tofu Tikka-Style Bowls with Basmati and Toasted Garlic Flatbreads
description: Creamy tikka sauce loaded with tofu, peas, peppers and onions is served with buttery basmati rice and warm garlic flatbread in this Indian-inspired dish.
